Description
  Write an OnSelectCancel event handler to respond when the selection in the list box is cancelled.
  For example, if you change property MultiSelect or Sorted, the list box cancels the selection in
  the list box, and triggers an OnSelectCancel event.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
